Introduction

Ella is a German/American-South Korean singer, dancer, model, and actress under The Black Label. She is a member of the South Korean girl group MEOVV.

Ella began her career as a model at age two, modelling for fashion brands such as H&M, Levi's, and GAP. She debuted on the runway at age nine at the Tokyo Girls Collection A/W 2018 fashion show held at Saitama Super Arena, Tokyo, Japan, in front of an audience of 30,000 viewers. Ella thereafter walked the runways of Tokyo Girls Collection S/S 2019 and 2019 New York Fashion Week.

On August 21, 2024, Ella was revealed as the first member of MEOVV. The group officially debuted on September 6, 2024, with their debut digital single "MEOW".
